---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="SaaS Cloud Infrastructure"
  descripcion="Multi-tenant cloud-native infrastructure for SaaS companies. Scalable Kubernetes platforms, tenant isolation, automated provisioning, and cost-per-tenant observability on AWS."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2540 0%, #0d2f50 100%); padding: 100px 24px 80px;">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8" style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.15); color: #60A5FA; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.25);">
        Industry · SaaS
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        Infrastructure that grows<br />with your customer base.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10" style="color: rgba(148,163,184,0.9);">
        Cloud-native platforms for SaaS companies — multi-tenant isolation, automated tenant provisioning, elastic scaling, and cost visibility per customer from day one.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-px" style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(30,111,255,0.4);">
          Design my SaaS platform
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/kubernetes-platforms" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all hover:bg-white/10" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);">
          Kubernetes platforms
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key points -->
  <section style="background: #F8FAFC; padding: 80px 24px;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #0A2540;">Platform capabilities for SaaS at scale</h2>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: #64748B;">From ten tenants to ten thousand — infrastructure that doesn't require engineering rewrites as you grow.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {[
          {
            title: 'Multi-tenant isolation patterns',
            desc: 'Namespace-per-tenant or cluster-per-tenant architectures with Kubernetes Network Policies, RBAC, and resource quotas enforced at the platform level. Tenant A cannot impact Tenant B.',
            icon: 'M3.75 6A2.25 2.25 0 016 3.75h2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0110.5 6v2.25a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H6a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6zM3.75 15.75A2.25 2.25 0 016 13.5h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 012.25 2.25V18a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H6A2.25 2.25 0 013.75 18v-2.25zM13.5 6a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25H18A2.25 2.25 0 0120.25 6v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 10.5h-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6zM13.5 15.75a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25H18a2.25 2.25 0 012.25 2.25V18A2.25 2.25 0 0118 20.25h-2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0113.5 18v-2.25z',
          },
          {
            title: 'Automated tenant provisioning',
            desc: 'New tenant onboarding via Terraform modules or Crossplane — database schemas, namespaces, IAM roles, and DNS records provisioned automatically in under 5 minutes.',
            icon: 'M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0l3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0013.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0113.803-3.7l3.181 3.182m0-4.991v4.99',
          },
          {
            title: 'Elastic autoscaling for demand spikes',
            desc: 'KEDA for event-driven autoscaling, HPA for pod scaling, and Karpenter for node provisioning. Handle 10x traffic spikes without pre-warming or manual intervention.',
            icon: 'M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z',
          },
          {
            title: 'Cost visibility per tenant',
            desc: 'AWS Cost Allocation Tags and Kubernetes resource tagging strategy for per-tenant cost attribution. Know exactly what each customer costs before you set your pricing.',
            icon: 'M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z',
          },
        ].map(({ title, desc, icon }) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7" style="border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06); box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(15,23,42,0.04);">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5" style="background: #EEF4FF;">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" style="color: #1E6FFF;" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d={icon} />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #0A2540;">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">{desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: #0A2540; padding: 80px 24px;">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to build a platform that scales with your SaaS?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-10" style="color: rgba(148,163,184,0.85);">Schedule a platform design session. We'll map your tenant model and design infrastructure that scales without engineering rewrites.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-px" style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(30,111,255,0.45);">
        Design my SaaS platform
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
